Wildrider leaps out of Astrotrain, landind crouched on the ground. "Ha
ha ahah, come out come out wherever you are." he yelled, as he raised
his gun, and pulled the trigger sending a stream of lasers into the air.
He then aimed at the ship, and sent a stream heading towards it, then
another behind him.
